## Why This License?

This system was born from psychiatric crisis, medication trials, suicidal ideation, and the desperate need for better self-advocacy tools. It represents years of lived experience distilled into actionable tracking protocols.

**The CC BY-NC 4.0 license ensures:**
- Anyone who needs it can access it FREE
- Mental health professionals can use it with patients
- It cannot be exploited commercially
- The creator receives proper attribution
- The work remains accessible to those who need it most

**If you want to use this commercially**, contact the creator to discuss licensing arrangements.

---

**Track your truth. Protect your wellbeing. Share freely, but ethically.**
